{"tid":699055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文明用語] 有 小學 力推「普教數」及「普教全科」","createTime":"2018-06-12T08:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T08:29:19.000Z","uid":53060,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39a92c92759904d62a2d7ba9dcf48b252a5a052e","tid":699055,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i63.tinypic.com/21ouc82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi63.tinypic.com%2F21ouc82.jpg&h=2d99e854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i65.tinypic.com/4tsn7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi65.tinypic.com%2F4tsn7b.jpg&h=5054a074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【撰文：曾焯文】<br />\n<br />\n《開罐Opener》近日訪問了約三十名小學生，發覺<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其學校不單普教中，甚至用普通話教其他科目，例如數學</strong></span>。這些兒童於是覺得香港粵語並非學習知識的語言（「普通話用來教學，廣東話用來鬧人」），日常即使講粵語，都會用普通話的詞彙（如「冷氣」變「空調」；「扮晒嘢」變「裝B」，按：B/逼乃北方粗口屄的諧音）；情況漸似今日的廣州。今日的廣州人，覺得粵語難登大雅之堂，大部份不諳講粵語，即使識講些少粵語，都多用普通話詞彙（如冰箱變雪櫃），而且用普通話句式（如食煞佢講成把它吃光），有普通話口音（如瑞士讀銳士，轟轟烈烈讀兇兇烈烈）。一種語言，一套世界觀（Lera Boroditsky 2010）。香港學校繼續以普通話為教學語言，代表香港靈魂的香港粵語好快淪亡。應對方法係大家日日夜夜講香港粵語，用香港粵語創作，大力杯葛普教中，並且質問教育局，所謂兩文三語教育政策，究竟為香港粵語教育做了何事？"},{"pid":"932f14870d1778ddaf39f3109a95d15db73aa628","tid":699055,"uid":53060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i68.tinypic.com/wag750.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi68.tinypic.com%2Fwag750.jpg&h=6b3ca785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i68.tinypic.com/v5fpk2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi68.tinypic.com%2Fv5fpk2.jpg&h=cc8a41f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25a5d151f68e02d80ce13bfeaeb8038baf322dea","tid":699055,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i63.tinypic.com/29apkk3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi63.tinypic.com%2F29apkk3.jpg&h=7b5e79bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i65.tinypic.com/etffvo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi65.tinypic.com%2Fetffvo.jpg&h=1ad26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f60e6248d6af2d41e7b3d3fdab6d07ba7c7699db","tid":699055,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"2fa29e21ab1e66dfeebdabfc3f7593abfbd97988","tid":699055,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:07:24.000Z","msg":"幾時用普通話教英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb56ac6e9d0cafbf98c9a0a2b3d0c2594fac811","tid":699055,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"即使識講些少粵語，都多用普通話詞彙（如<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>冰箱變雪櫃</strong></span>）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪我見識少，唔係一直都叫開雪櫃咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc5fc20434336c7ddedbd78a3ee2e5c3c1c93b4","tid":699055,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2fa29e21ab1e66dfeebdabfc3f7593abfbd97988","tid":699055,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:07:24.000Z","msg":"幾時用普通話教英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/232648_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F232648_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=f10d38f1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}